{"tid":834446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【又贏】張學友演唱會現違法航拍機　大陸警方出動大炮迫降","createTime":"2018-09-24T08:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T10:05:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"17270edd4c932ef859c343d4d80517f572c194b5","tid":834446,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-09-23-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.09.48-694x369.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-09-23-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.09.48-694x369.png&h=fe830585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張學友巡迴演唱會日前轉戰至四川遂寧舉行，不少大陸歌迷到場觀賞歌神演出。不過在 21 日演唱會舉行期間，上空出現兩部懷疑違法航拍機，其後當地警方當場舉槍迫降，過程中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n在大約晚上 9 時 30 分左右，有民眾目擊警方當場舉起類似手提大炮之物體，指向航拍機。警方看似確認在航拍機下面沒有觀眾的情況下，當場利用反無人機裝置，使兩架航拍機安全降落，並帶返警署扣查，以違反公眾安全查辦。根據《梨視頻》影片所見「大炮」<span style=\"color: red;\">並無發射實彈</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/09/23/droneinconcertchina/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2Fdroneinconcertchina%2Flife-tech%2F&d=bVbFEPqeSkte1NQq8Yo1yk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=97548859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/09/23/droneinconcertchina/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"1e96e000645cac632ae368226014249a74e450cc","tid":834446,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-09-23-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.00.14-694x489.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-09-23-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.00.14-694x489.png&h=59526